WEBVTT

00:00.989 --> 00:02.989
<i>Previously on</i> Proven Innocent...

00:03.062 --> 00:04.729
What happened between you and Rosemary?

00:04.780 --> 00:05.884
You're afraid of me?

00:05.953 --> 00:07.564
MADELINE: <i>It is my privilege</i>

00:07.601 --> 00:09.324
to announce the candidacy

00:09.344 --> 00:11.398
of Evan Esteban-Miller

00:11.435 --> 00:13.462
<i>for the attorney general of Ill...</i>

00:13.515 --> 00:15.848
Are the rumors true
about your marriage?

00:15.885 --> 00:17.925
But aren't you tired of
hiding our relationship?

00:18.019 --> 00:19.260
- Aah!
- NIKKI: <i>I'm a cop, Bodie.</i>

00:19.354 --> 00:21.579
There's more to your
identity than just prison.

00:21.616 --> 00:22.735
There is, huh?

00:22.772 --> 00:23.988
<i>And what would that be?</i>

00:24.025 --> 00:26.247
I missed you.
You were the first love of my life.

00:26.284 --> 00:27.860
WREN: <i>We spent a long time together.</i>

00:28.020 --> 00:29.820
<i>Those were the best years of my life.</i>

00:34.700 --> 00:38.227
You can't be serious.
The police can't find her?

00:38.264 --> 00:39.930
You're letting them get away with that.

00:40.227 --> 00:42.166
Your Honor, give me two days.

00:42.211 --> 00:44.344
My investigator will bring
her right to this spot,

00:44.381 --> 00:45.657
just please don't dismiss this case.

00:45.694 --> 00:47.210
Miss Scott, I already decided.

00:47.247 --> 00:49.510
I have filed countless affidavits.

00:49.547 --> 00:51.930
I have multiple witnesses,
and I have laid out

00:51.967 --> 00:55.034
in exact detail what Mrs.
Ramirez said to me,

00:55.071 --> 00:56.556
has said to dozens of people.

00:56.593 --> 00:59.644
How she and her family have
been harassed, intimidated,

00:59.681 --> 01:01.547
threatened with jail time

01:01.584 --> 01:04.427
and deportation,
and now suddenly they can't find her?

01:04.464 --> 01:06.188
You can't be okay with that.

01:06.225 --> 01:08.449
- Miss Scott, that's enough.
- Put me on the stand.

01:08.486 --> 01:10.246
- I'll tell you what happened.
- I said that's enough.

01:10.282 --> 01:12.610
Or better yet, call the corrupt police

01:12.657 --> 01:14.430
who continue to harass

01:14.467 --> 01:17.059
and intimidate my witnesses.
That includes

01:17.096 --> 01:20.088
and is particularly directed
to Detective Falcone

01:20.125 --> 01:21.639
and his flunkies, who seem

01:21.666 --> 01:24.733
to conveniently have the entire
legal system just wrapped around

01:24.770 --> 01:26.141
their fat little fingers.

01:26.178 --> 01:27.618
It's absolutely outrageous.

01:27.655 --> 01:28.935
You know what? You people make me sick.

01:28.971 --> 01:30.399
One more word and I
hold you in contempt.

01:30.436 --> 01:32.188
Yeah, well, I hold you in contempt.

01:32.336 --> 01:36.252
- [GATE ALARM BUZZES]
- EASY: Feel better now?

01:36.782 --> 01:38.287
Yeah, just about.

01:38.477 --> 01:40.495
You know, I'll deny I ever said it,

01:40.532 --> 01:43.585
but a part of me...
a very small part of me...

01:43.914 --> 01:45.663
- relaxes in here.
- Yeah,

01:45.700 --> 01:48.149
it's like Tahiti,
without the everything.

01:48.225 --> 01:49.541
The iron bars,

01:49.578 --> 01:52.961
the rules and regulations...
it's familiar.

01:53.335 --> 01:54.947
You keep picking fights
with Judge Riley,

01:54.984 --> 01:56.325
you'll never have to leave.

01:56.754 --> 01:58.649
He's one of the judges that
still thinks you're guilty.

01:58.686 --> 02:00.406
He's also a misogynist pig.

02:00.443 --> 02:02.289
Who runs unopposed every six years.

02:02.326 --> 02:04.865
Easy, their key witness was
paid off by a corrupt cop

02:04.902 --> 02:06.204
to lie on the stand.

02:06.287 --> 02:07.743
And Falcone's gonna keep paying off

02:07.780 --> 02:09.446
witnesses unless we stop him.

02:09.483 --> 02:12.063
So what are you saying, you want
to take down Detective Falcone?

02:12.108 --> 02:16.024
Exactly. Let's expose him for
the corrupt cop that he is.

02:16.086 --> 02:17.649
You know, I bet if we took him down,

02:17.686 --> 02:20.297
dozens of his wrongful
convictions would be tossed out.

02:20.439 --> 02:23.663
Falcone is a high-level cop
with friends in high places.

02:23.907 --> 02:26.860
Taking him down would
require an IAD investigation.

02:26.897 --> 02:30.602
Or just one case,
one solid witness to expose him.

02:30.710 --> 02:32.094
You want to start a war.

02:32.131 --> 02:34.044
We're already fighting the war, Easy.

02:34.295 --> 02:35.778
Let's friggin' win it.

02:37.182 --> 02:39.141
I just need you to post my bail first.

02:39.995 --> 02:41.770
It's what I live for.

02:43.245 --> 02:45.228
[GATE ALARM BUZZES]

02:46.859 --> 02:50.299
♪ ♪

