42:05.368 --> 42:08.067
Baby... Baby,
you know that Falcone was dirty.

42:08.104 --> 42:09.383
Don't!

42:09.960 --> 42:13.070
Did you even think about how
this would blow back on me?

42:14.815 --> 42:16.627
Yeah, I didn't think so.

42:16.755 --> 42:20.284
- Nikki, wait.
- No. Damn it, Bodie.

42:22.513 --> 42:24.454
I liked you.

42:25.609 --> 42:27.442
Why'd you have to ruin this?

42:28.283 --> 42:29.507
[DOOR CLOSES]

42:29.667 --> 42:31.400
VIOLET: <i>If we can sit and listen</i>

42:31.461 --> 42:33.337
<i>to our enemies' points of view,</i>

42:33.374 --> 42:35.591
we can maybe learn something

42:36.216 --> 42:37.757
about each other

42:38.106 --> 42:40.075
and about ourselves.

42:40.598 --> 42:42.744
So please, guys,

42:43.088 --> 42:45.652
let's keep this conversation going.

42:46.786 --> 42:48.961
<i>No matter how hard it is to do.</i>

42:52.052 --> 42:54.440
